5
00:00:08,881 --> 00:00:10,181
Keep an eye on the case.

6
00:00:10,181 --> 00:00:11,581
He sees through the one and only truth.

7
00:00:11,581 --> 00:00:13,181
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

